kocur.lina.agent

Class Lina

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent.BaseAgentController
      • kocur.lina.agent.Lina
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent.AgentController, cz.cuni.mff.kocur.configuration.ConfigurationChangeListener, cz.cuni.mff.kocur.console.Controllable

    public class Lina
extends cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent.BaseAgentController
    Class that implements our Lina agent. The agent is capable of playing any lane. First thing it does is that it goes to pickup a rune. Then it farms the lane, attacks buildings and heroes, while trying to keep away from the threats and moving towards the farm.
    Author:
    kocur
